questionResult_name: How Many Kids Will You Have

answersResultList.title: One.
answersResultList.resultContent: A big family just isn't a priority, so having one child is most likely your fate. And this might not even be a traditional child... a pet may make your parental dreams come true.

answersResultList.title: Two.
answersResultList.resultContent: We're guessing you will have two children. Maybe even twins! For you, two will be the perfect balance. They can play together, and you have two hands to hold them with. Perfect! Two pets would work, too.
